{
  "texts": [
    "Since deep learning technology was introduced into the field of video understanding, the task of TAD has developed rapidly.",
    "In this study, 1326 articles relating to TAD from the past 12 years were retrieved via a Web of Science search for temporal action detection (TAD) and temporal action localization (TAL).",
    "As shown in Fig. 8, a keyword heatmap was created.",
    "The larger the circle, the more times the keyword appears.",
    "The round layer from the inside out represents the past to the present, and the redder the layer, the more attractive popular it is."
  ]
}